Item: Glistering shortsword
Coder: Goldberry
Pathname:  /d/Terel/dabaay/weapon/dshort.c
Skill Enhancement: None
Type: Weapon Sword
          Hit: 45
          Pen: 42
Magic: 62, enchantment
Magic Resistance: None
Limitations: Requires (SS_WEP_SWORD/3 + SS_DEX/2) >= 75
            and 0 intox to wield.
Specials:   Does extra damage to intoxicated targets.
            On a random(12)>3 against a target with
            query_intoxicated > 0, it will do additional
            damage equal to the target's percentage of
            intoxication (query_intoxicated/intoxicated_max)
            multiplied by the initial hit.
            Max damage is dam * 2
Game Location: /d/Terel/dabaay/npc/slugg.c


